  <div id="app" class="page-moviemarket"><div class="movie-market-page" style="background-color:#20565f"><div class="poster-box"><img class="img noneBg poster-img block" src="https://obj.pipi.cn/tangram/a225a908c0535cd05696ab2fa477783d.jpg?imageView2/2/w/750/q/80" e="1" l="1"><div class="bg want"><img class="img noneBg want-icon" src="//obj.pipi.cn/festatic/common/image/ecf081f8d6d344a99b61e326902c130e.gif"><span class="txt">想看</span><span class="num">39.74万</span></div><div class="bg share"><img class="img noneBg share-icon" src="//obj.pipi.cn/festatic/common/image/8db77ade1feb2287b0387c3644ca75be.png"><span class="txt">分享</span><span class="num">21.47万</span></div></div><img class="img noneBg movie-btn" src="https://obj.pipi.cn/tangram/1b4672cf3a74e76244014c6e1cc64771.jpg?imageView2/2/w/674/q/80" e="1" l="1"><div class="video-play-wrap"><img class="img noneBg video-play-bg" src="https://obj.pipi.cn/tangram/17f4a945485226f51986aa7c9fe3acca.jpg?imageView2/2/w/750"><div class="video-container" style="top:21.333333333333332vw" data-view-bid="" data-lab=""><video webkit-playsinline="true" x5-playsinline="true" playsinline="" x-webkit-airplay="deny" src="https://vod.pipi.cn/fec9203cvodtransbj1251246104/4624dce05576678019543189878/v.f42905.mp4" poster="https://p0.pipi.cn/friday/58b189b31b167c14b63633cd417ce255.jpg?imageMogr2/thumbnail/2500x2500%3E" loop=""></video><img class="img noneBg video-poster" src="https://p0.pipi.cn/friday/58b189b31b167c14b63633cd417ce255.jpg?imageView2/1/w/659/h/366" e="1" c="1" l="1"><div class="video-title">电影《封神第一部》发布特殊道具特辑</div><img class="img noneBg play-btn" src="//obj.pipi.cn/festatic/common/image/cecf734382fb1928924bf38257a9be6f.png"></div></div><div class="interact"><div class="interact-container"><div class="topic" data-view-bid="b_movie_xk6nh67a_mv" data-lab="{&quot;topic_id&quot;:&quot;176544132&quot;,&quot;custom&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:1128}}"><img class="img noneBg topic-bg-img" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7"><div class="topic-container"><div class="title"><img class="img noneBg well-icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7"><span class="well-txt" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">你最喜欢“封神”中的哪个角色？</span></div><div class="btn" style="background-color: rgb(242, 191, 127); color: rgb(125, 74, 22);"><img class="img noneBg flow-icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7"><span class="flow-txt">开榜封神</span></div><div class="count">已有 17888 人走进神话世界</div></div></div><div class="discuss" data-view-bid="b_movie_iy98f6az_mv" data-lab="{&quot;topic_id&quot;:&quot;176544132&quot;}" style="background-color: rgb(71, 107, 127);"><div class="swiper-container-discuss swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-vertical swiper-container-android"><div class="swiper-wrapper" style="transition-duration: 0ms; transform: translate3d(0px, -90px, 0px);"><a href="maoyan://maoyan.com/movie/hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" class="swiper-slide swiper-slide-duplicate" data-event="maoyan:__maoyan.com_movie_hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" to="maoyan://maoyan.com/movie/hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" data-bid="b_fb4li6os" data-lab="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;comment&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:27,&quot;topic_id&quot;:&quot;176544132&quot;,&quot;custom&quot;:{&quot;region&quot;:7,&quot;id&quot;:1181789408}}" data-swiper-slide-index="27" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); height: 30px;"><img class="img noneBg avatar" src="//p1.meituan.net/maoyanuser/da1d6e35eda3d36bd7c61a60ea7f942a10407.png@80q_1e_1c" e="1" c="1">：<span class="content">直说自己的真实感受，封神场面很大，个人感觉很多故事情节处理的很高级。纣王和妲己的荒淫无道处理的很好，感觉不到演员角色的色情低俗，明知道是男女荒淫的反面人物，导演拍摄处理的很智慧，画面呈现的结果真的很高级。
姜皇后被杀的戏份改变的点感觉处理的也很好-直面惋惜。
印象最重的戏份是四位伯侯被殷寿当堂逼迫质子们弑父，能明显对比出西伯侯的睿智和沉稳。
虽然不懂什么舞蹈，但是娜然扮演妲己的表演真的可圈可点。这是明显靠表演出圈的妲己。不再是靠颜值和装扮出戏的妲己。导演靠自己的能力表达出了他所想要的妲己。
个人浅显的认为，封神每一个喷雾刻画的都很成功，给导演点赞！</span></a><a href="maoyan://maoyan.com/movie/hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" class="swiper-slide swiper-slide-duplicate" data-event="maoyan:__maoyan.com_movie_hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" to="maoyan://maoyan.com/movie/hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" data-bid="b_fb4li6os" data-lab="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;comment&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:28,&quot;topic_id&quot;:&quot;176544132&quot;,&quot;custom&quot;:{&quot;region&quot;:7,&quot;id&quot;:1181774665}}" data-swiper-slide-index="28" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); height: 30px;"><img class="img noneBg avatar" src="//p1.meituan.net/avatar/ffe7e55ef5dac1cab7308e6866db5fc511510.jpg@80q_1e_1c" e="1" c="1">：<span class="content">非常好看！很喜欢质子团</span></a><a href="maoyan://maoyan.com/movie/hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" class="swiper-slide swiper-slide-duplicate swiper-slide-prev" data-event="maoyan:__maoyan.com_movie_hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" to="maoyan://maoyan.com/movie/hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" data-bid="b_fb4li6os" data-lab="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;comment&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:29,&quot;topic_id&quot;:&quot;176544132&quot;,&quot;custom&quot;:{&quot;region&quot;:7,&quot;id&quot;:1181788472}}" data-swiper-slide-index="29" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); height: 30px;"><img class="img noneBg avatar" src="//p1.meituan.net/avatar/80eb775c8bb1ab3fd508d65ab73d80b523902.jpg@80q_1e_1c" e="1" c="1">：<span class="content">还挺不错的，时间过的很快。姜子牙印象中是个瘦瘦的老头，有点违和，不过也还行吧。姬昌的扮演者虽然我挺喜欢的，奈何生病语音不是特别清晰。</span></a><a href="maoyan://maoyan.com/movie/hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" class="swiper-slide swiper-slide-active" data-event="maoyan:__maoyan.com_movie_hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" to="maoyan://maoyan.com/movie/hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" data-bid="b_fb4li6os" data-lab="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;comment&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:0,&quot;topic_id&quot;:&quot;176544132&quot;,&quot;custom&quot;:{&quot;region&quot;:7,&quot;id&quot;:1181809023}}" data-swiper-slide-index="0" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); height: 30px;"><img class="img noneBg avatar" src="//p0.meituan.net/maoyanuser/107702336ac18d9b9313e9b003020c5914743.png@80q_1e_1c" e="1" c="1">：<span class="content">满满的细节、满满的诚意。期待后面两部。话说，好多人都去影院二刷三刷了，票房是被压了么？</span></a><a href="maoyan://maoyan.com/movie/hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" class="swiper-slide swiper-slide-next" data-event="maoyan:__maoyan.com_movie_hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" to="maoyan://maoyan.com/movie/hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" data-bid="b_fb4li6os" data-lab="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;comment&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:1,&quot;topic_id&quot;:&quot;176544132&quot;,&quot;custom&quot;:{&quot;region&quot;:7,&quot;id&quot;:1181785702}}" data-swiper-slide-index="1" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); height: 30px;"><img class="img noneBg avatar" src="//p1.meituan.net/maoyanuser/e3e7cc3a9c73cad68c4ba5a33f2913584741.jpg@80q_1e_1c" e="1" c="1">：<span class="content">我和孩子太喜欢看了，我们刚刚二刷，还是很震撼！期待二三部！</span></a><a href="maoyan://maoyan.com/movie/hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" class="swiper-slide" data-event="maoyan:__maoyan.com_movie_hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" to="maoyan://maoyan.com/movie/hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" data-bid="b_fb4li6os" data-lab="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;comment&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:2,&quot;topic_id&quot;:&quot;176544132&quot;,&quot;custom&quot;:{&quot;region&quot;:7,&quot;id&quot;:1181791577}}" data-swiper-slide-index="2" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); height: 30px;"><img class="img noneBg avatar" src="//p0.meituan.net/avatar/c79d184f4fc6d338f9d677016edcdeb87386.jpg@80q_1e_1c" e="1" c="1">：<span class="content">演技很好👍</span></a><a href="maoyan://maoyan.com/movie/hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" class="swiper-slide" data-event="maoyan:__maoyan.com_movie_hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" to="maoyan://maoyan.com/movie/hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" data-bid="b_fb4li6os" data-lab="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;comment&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:3,&quot;topic_id&quot;:&quot;176544132&quot;,&quot;custom&quot;:{&quot;region&quot;:7,&quot;id&quot;:181787772}}" data-swiper-slide-index="3" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); height: 30px;"><img class="img noneBg avatar" src="//p0.meituan.net/avatar/811a9d6c045a35c41247f275c7a98e9b12062.jpg@80q_1e_1c" e="1" c="1">：<span class="content">太好看啦</span></a><a href="maoyan://maoyan.com/movie/hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" class="swiper-slide" data-event="maoyan:__maoyan.com_movie_hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" to="maoyan://maoyan.com/movie/hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" data-bid="b_fb4li6os" data-lab="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;comment&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:4,&quot;topic_id&quot;:&quot;176544132&quot;,&quot;custom&quot;:{&quot;region&quot;:7,&quot;id&quot;:1181776772}}" data-swiper-slide-index="4" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); height: 30px;"><img class="img noneBg avatar" src="//p0.meituan.net/avatar/374042f53486acb19087d1f48fb47ea718783.jpg@80q_1e_1c" e="1" c="1">：<span class="content">画面还可以，但剧情结束得有些突然，哪个角色都没有结局，看懵了
虽然是为第二部做铺垫，但是主角都没什么结局，感觉看了第一部像没看</span></a><a href="maoyan://maoyan.com/movie/hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" class="swiper-slide" data-event="maoyan:__maoyan.com_movie_hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" to="maoyan://maoyan.com/movie/hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" data-bid="b_fb4li6os" data-lab="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;comment&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:5,&quot;topic_id&quot;:&quot;176544132&quot;,&quot;custom&quot;:{&quot;region&quot;:7,&quot;id&quot;:1181775837}}" data-swiper-slide-index="5" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); height: 30px;"><img class="img noneBg avatar" src="//p1.meituan.net/maoyanuser/bc5fc2d9138de62a33edebea8f6e21795253.jpg@80q_1e_1c" e="1" c="1">：<span class="content">特效超棒，赶上国际先进水平了，演员演技很好，小鲜肉充满阳刚之气，真正的男子汉阳刚之美，不再是现在的奶狗白幼瘦了，终于看到了一部正常审美观的电影，苏妲己的演员演技不错，把一只报恩的狐狸演的很单位，苏妲己在这部剧里不再只是一个外表好看的坏女人。期待第二部早日上映！</span></a><a href="maoyan://maoyan.com/movie/hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" class="swiper-slide" data-event="maoyan:__maoyan.com_movie_hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" to="maoyan://maoyan.com/movie/hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" data-bid="b_fb4li6os" data-lab="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;comment&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:6,&quot;topic_id&quot;:&quot;176544132&quot;,&quot;custom&quot;:{&quot;region&quot;:7,&quot;id&quot;:1181794439}}" data-swiper-slide-index="6" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); height: 30px;"><img class="img noneBg avatar" src="//p0.meituan.net/avatar/fe619f5203aa2071c3883af07b23c7ad11257.jpg@80q_1e_1c" e="1" c="1">：<span class="content">好喜欢！好看，震撼！期待2,3,</span></a><a href="maoyan://maoyan.com/movie/hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" class="swiper-slide" data-event="maoyan:__maoyan.com_movie_hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" to="maoyan://maoyan.com/movie/hotTopicLists?movieid=346288&amp;topicid=176544132" data-bid="b_fb4li6os" data-lab="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;comment&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:7,